* Models provided by CGD are based on typical device 
* performance, CGD models, therefore, do not warrant full and 
* accurate representations of all the specifications or 
* operating characteristics of the related semiconductor 
* products. Neither is CGD responsible for validating or 
* verifying simulation results in all application environments. 
* CGD models are behavioural models. 
* Models are widely used to evaluate device performance but 
* they cannot model exact device performance under all 
* conditions, neither are they designed to replace prototyping 
* or verification. CGD provide the simulation models and data
* 'as is' and without any representations or warranties, 
